{"tid":1968824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門醫院21歲女成為本港最年輕的深切治療部病人","createTime":"2020-04-12T03:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T04:55:35.000Z","uid":346581,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e572da1b38958a4b18ca212a957215f860f79930","tid":1968824,"uid":346581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎確診數字連日回落。昨日（11日）下午4時的過去24小時，新增11宗確診。而由昨午4時至今，至少再多3宗初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n●威院63歲女：第902號患者、61歲男子的密切接觸者。第902號個案原居英國，3月24日返港。暫時未知該63歲女子有否外遊，或被第902號個案在家居隔離期間傳染。<br />\n●屯門醫院21歲女：第956號患者、28歲男子的妹妹。第956號個案是加拿大留學生，在屯門醫院深切治療部留醫，是目前本港最年輕的深切治療部病人。暫未知該21歲女子有否外遊紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 蘋果"},{"pid":"f07b72d9cd1ed6ffc7d6de40829b54d0c33830fe","tid":1968824,"uid":19372,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"依一刻 唔知佢呀哥係咩心情"},{"pid":"b1322d978dcfce828ae39bce3c2b6e395a96bd03","tid":1968824,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"衛生署唔可以去入境處查？"},{"pid":"f43c26b1b700a22e935559d62e06f521bd8612c3","tid":1968824,"uid":346581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b29c478dd041bd4d718cf75c7c818ba8954e2c","tid":1968824,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"東張西望不如訪問下佢阿哥"},{"pid":"4fd8c91e848750ec2bf5f3c2844daf3ae630dd28","tid":1968824,"uid":97989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"寫到1999<br />\n<br />\n第956號患者係哥定妹"},{"pid":"68aa98cb0a8fb9bd40d2af1ce5f8f6b73d2a7c9e","tid":1968824,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67b29c478dd041bd4d718cf75c7c818ba8954e2c","tid":1968824,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"東張西望不如訪問下佢阿哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"